# Brand Color Palette — Health Tracker PWA

All UI must use these exact hex values. Never use Tailwind semantic color classes like `blue-500`, `gray-200`, `purple-*`, `red-*`, `green-*`, `yellow-*`, `indigo-*`, or `emerald-*`.

## Palette

| Role | Hex | Usage |
|------|-----|-------|
| Primary blue | `#4A8FA8` | CTAs, active states, progress bars, links |
| Light blue | `#9DBFD0` | Gradient starts, tints, soft backgrounds |
| Dark blue | `#38788F` | Hover states, gradient ends |
| Sage green | `#3F6B40` | Completion only (checked boxes, done states) |
| Light sage | `#87A87C` | Sage gradients/accents |
| Cream border | `#EDE8DC` | All card borders, dividers, input borders |
| Page bg | `#FDFAF6` | Page backgrounds |
| Text primary | `#1C1C1E` | Headings, body |
| Text secondary | `#8E8E93` | Subtitles, labels, metadata |
| Text muted | `#C7C7CC` | Placeholders, disabled |
| Dark surface | `#2C2C2E` | Dark mode inputs |
| Dark border | `#38383A` | Dark mode borders |

## Rules

```tsx
// ❌ NEVER use Tailwind semantic colors
className="bg-blue-500 text-gray-700 border-red-200"
className="from-purple-50 to-indigo-100"

// ✅ ALWAYS use brand hex values
className="bg-[#4A8FA8] text-[#8E8E93] border-[#EDE8DC]"
className="from-[#9DBFD0] to-[#4A8FA8]"
```

## Common Patterns

```tsx
// CTA button
className="bg-[#4A8FA8] hover:bg-[#38788F] text-white"

// Ghost/tint button
className="bg-[#4A8FA8]/10 text-[#4A8FA8] hover:bg-[#4A8FA8]/15"

// Card
className="bg-white dark:bg-[#1C1C1E] rounded-2xl border border-[#EDE8DC] dark:border-[#38383A]"

// Progress bar track
className="bg-[#EDE8DC] dark:bg-[#38383A]"

// Progress bar fill (primary)
className="bg-[#4A8FA8]"

// Completion (done/checked)
className="bg-[#3F6B40] border-[#3F6B40] text-white"

// Active bottom nav
className="text-[#4A8FA8]"

// Input focus ring
className="focus:ring-[#4A8FA8] focus:border-[#4A8FA8]"

// Muted info panel (e.g. stop conditions)
className="bg-[#9DBFD0]/10 border-[#9DBFD0]/20"
```

## Never Use
- `shadow-xl`, `shadow-2xl`, `shadow-3xl` (use no shadow or `shadow-sm` only)
- Any `bg-gray-*`, `text-gray-*`, `border-gray-*`
- Any `blue-*`, `purple-*`, `indigo-*`, `red-*`, `green-*`, `yellow-*`, `emerald-*`
- Hardcoded gradients unless from→to uses only brand hex values above
